headline: Carenet Health Named Major Contender in Everest Group's 2025 PEAK Matrix® for Care Management Platforms
summary: SAN ANTONIO, Texas, September 30, 2025--Carenet Health has been recognized as a Major Contender in Everest Group's 2025 PEAK Matrix® Assessment for Clinical and Care Management (CCM) Operations Platforms for Payers. This prestigious recognition reinforces Carenet's position as a leading healthcare technology partner, empowering payers to achieve measurable improvements in engagement, efficiency, and meaningful business and health outcomes.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks with Competitive Advantages and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.
